{"id": "art-301", "label": "Art. 301", "title": "Art. 301: Folosirea funcţiei pentru favorizarea unor persoane", "slug": "art-301", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_297978573\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1145\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_297978573\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 301:\nFolosirea func&#355;iei pentru favorizarea unor persoane </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1547271386\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1144\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1547271386\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Fapta func&#355;ionarului public care, în exercitarea\natribu&#355;iilor de serviciu, a îndeplinit un act prin care s-a ob&#355;inut\nun folos patrimonial pentru sine, pentru so&#355;ul s&#259;u, pentru o\nrud&#259; ori un afin pân&#259; la gradul II inclusiv se pedepse&#351;te cu\nînchisoarea de la unu la 5 ani &#351;i interzicerea exercit&#259;rii dreptului\nde a ocupa o func&#355;ie public&#259; pe o perioad&#259; de 3 ani.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_780312529\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1143\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_780312529\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Dispozi&#355;iile\nalin. (1) nu se aplic&#259; în cazurile în care actul sau decizia se\nrefer&#259; la urm&#259;toarele situa&#355;ii:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_408450472\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1142\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_408450472\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)emiterea, aprobarea sau adoptarea actelor normative;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_45489829\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1141\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_45489829\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)exercitarea unui drept recunoscut de lege sau în\nîndeplinirea unei obliga&#355;ii impuse de lege, cu respectarea\ncondi&#355;iilor &#351;i limitelor prev&#259;zute de aceasta.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}